    <script type="text/javascript">
        $(document).ready(function() {
            $('.select .select-container div:nth-child(' + ($('.tab.current', '#section6').index() + 1) + ')', '#section6').hide();
            
            $('.tab', '#section6').click(function() {
                $('.tab, .tab-content', '#section6').removeClass('current');
                $(this).addClass('current');
                $('.tab-content[data-id=' + $(this).data('id') + ']', '#section6').addClass('current');
                $('.tab-select .select-container div', '#section6').removeClass('current');
                $('.tab-select .select-container div:nth-child(' + ($(this).index() + 1) + ')', '#section6').addClass('current');
                chkContentHeight();
            });

            $('.tab-select', '#section6').change(function() {
                $('.tab, .tab-content', '#section6').removeClass('current');
                $('.tab[data-id=' + $(this).val() + ']', '#section6').addClass('current');
                $('.tab-content[data-id=' + $(this).val() + ']', '#section6').addClass('current');
                $('.tab-select .select-container div', '#section6').removeClass('current');
                $('.tab-select .select-container div:nth-child(' +  ($('.tab.current', '#section6').index() + 1) + ')', '#section6').addClass('current');
                $('.select .select-container div', '#section6').show();
                $('.select .select-container div:nth-child(' + ($('.tab.current', '#section6').index() + 1) + ')', '#section6').hide();
                chkContentHeight();
            });

            $('.record-slider', '#section6').Slider({
                slides: '.record-item',
                maxSlide: 1,
                swipeControl: true,
                skipBoundary: true,
                infiniteLoop: true
            });

            function chkContentHeight() {
                $('p.description', '#section6').each(function() {
                    if($(this).height() > 160) {
                        $(this).parent().addClass('more');
                    }
                });
            }
            chkContentHeight();

            $('.record-item article button.view-more', '#section6').click(function() {
                $(this).hide();
                $(this).parent().find('.view-less').show();
                $(this).parent().find('.description').hide();
                $(this).parent().find('.content').show();
            });
            $('.record-item article button.view-less', '#section6').click(function() {
                $(this).hide();
                $(this).parent().find('.view-more').show();
                $(this).parent().find('.description').show();
                $(this).parent().find('.content').hide();
            });
        });
    </script>
</section>
<section id="section7" data-total="10">
    <div class="container">
        <div class="section-title">
            <h2 class="colour2">What’s new at Glenealy School?</h2>
            <span class="bg-colour1"></span>
        </div>
    </div>
    <div class="record-slider">
        <div class="slider-container">
                            <div class="post-item">
                    <div class="post" data-id="336">
                        <time>24/03/2026</time>
                        <h3>🌳 What an incredible achievement in just one day! We worked together to create a wonderful new space to learn in the great outdoors! We build a pond, planted beautiful fruit trees, and positioned some natural outdoor furniture. We even had our first visitor…Gary the Snail! 🐌</h3>
                        <button>Read more</button>
                        <img src="/cache/img/a16c1ff03669341681d48cc5b837be62.jpg" alt="656702216_928775389521944_4536775076449976833_n" loading="lazy" width="682" height="682" />                    </div>
                </div>
                            <div class="post-item">
                    <div class="post" data-id="335">
                        <time>24/03/2026</time>
                        <h3>Tomorrow - one of the highlights of our year - The Year 6 PYP Exhibition 🎉<br><br>Here's a sneak peak of our video as we await the big day.<br><br>👀</h3>
                        <button>Read more</button>
                        <img src="/cache/img/14a9a68d948f77ca8906ebd9935a7a59.jpg" alt="655156526_1288362653238862_3023786054741097316_n" loading="lazy" width="682" height="682" />                    </div>
                </div>
                            <div class="post-item">
                    <div class="post" data-id="334">
                        <time>24/03/2026</time>
                        <h3>🪴 It’s been a very busy morning of hauling, shovelling, raking and pouring as we work together to create our Outdoor Classroom. It’s already looking fantastic, and we’ve only just begun!</h3>
